creator: Vachel Lindsay
description:
LibriVox recording of The Chinese Nightingale and Other Poems by Vachel Lindsay.
Read in English by Tony Addison; Ezwa; Newgatenovelist; Melissa Hoffman; Dini Steyn; Amabam; Alexandra Helms; Crystal Rogers; Larry Wilson; Diana Schmidt; Nancee Cline; Kathleen Moore; Kristin Gjerløw
This is a collection of poems on various topics by Vachel Lindsay.
Please note that the Booker T. Washington trilogy had to be omitted from this collection. - Summary by Carolin
For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording.

For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org.
